SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ClassId], [c].[ClassShiftId], [c].[CourseId], [c].[CreateDay], [c].[DayOfWeek], [c].[EndDay], [c].[RoomId], [c].[StartDay], [c].[Status], [c0].[Id], [c0].[ClassName], [c0].[CreateDay], [c0].[FacultyId], [c0].[Status], [c1].[Id], [l].[Id], [r].[Id], [c2].[Id], [s0].[Id], [s0].[Address], [s0].[BirthDate], [s0].[CCCD], [s0].[ClassId], [s0].[CreateDay], [s0].[Email], [s0].[FullName], [s0].[Gender], [s0].[Image], [s0].[PhoneNumber], [s0].[Status], [s0].[StudentCode], [c1].[CourseName], [c1].[CreateDay], [c1].[LecturerId], [c1].[SchoolYear], [c1].[Semester], [c1].[Status], [c1].[SubjectId], [l].[Address], [l].[BirthDate], [l].[Cccd], [l].[CreateDay], [l].[Email], [l].[FacultyId], [l].[FullName], [l].[Gender], [l].[Image], [l].[LecturerCode], [l].[PhoneNumber], [l].[Status], [r].[Building], [r].[CreateDay], [r].[Floor], [r].[Name], [r].[Status], [r].[Vacuity], [c2].[CreateDay], [c2].[EndTime], [c2].[Name], [c2].[StartTime], [c2].[Status]
FROM [ClassSchedule] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Student] AS [s0] ON [c0].[Id] = [s0].[ClassId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Student] AS [s]
    WHERE [c0].[Id] = [s].[ClassId] AND [s].[StudentCode] = @__username_0)
ORDER BY [c].[EndDay] DESC, [c].[Id], [c0].[Id], [c1].[Id], [l].[Id], [r].[Id], [c2].[Id]

FROM [ClassSchedule] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Student] AS [s0] ON [c0].[Id] = [s0].[ClassId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Student] AS [s]
    WHERE [c0].[Id] = [s].[ClassId] AND [s].[StudentCode] = @__username_0) AND [c].[StartDay] <= @__endOfWeek_1 AND [c].[EndDay] >= @__startOfWeek_2 AND [c].[Status] = CAST(1 AS bit)

FROM [ClassSchedule] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Student] AS [s0] ON [c0].[Id] = [s0].[ClassId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Student] AS [s]
    WHERE [c0].[Id] = [s].[ClassId] AND [s].[StudentCode] = @__username_0)

FROM [ClassSchedule] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Student] AS [s0] ON [c0].[Id] = [s0].[ClassId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Student] AS [s]
    WHERE [c0].[Id] = [s].[ClassId] AND [s].[StudentCode] = @__username_0) AND [c].[StartDay] <= @__endOfWeek_1 AND [c].[EndDay] >= @__startOfWeek_2 AND [c].[Status] = CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ClassId], [c].[ClassShiftId], [c].[CourseId], [c].[CreateDay], [c].[DayOfWeek], [c].[EndDay], [c].[RoomId], [c].[StartDay], [c].[Status], [c0].[Id], [c0].[ClassName], [c0].[CreateDay], [c0].[FacultyId], [c0].[Status], [c1].[Id], [l].[Id], [r].[Id], [c2].[Id], [s0].[Id], [s0].[Address], [s0].[BirthDate], [s0].[CCCD], [s0].[ClassId], [s0].[CreateDay], [s0].[Email], [s0].[FullName], [s0].[Gender], [s0].[Image], [s0].[PhoneNumber], [s0].[Status], [s0].[StudentCode], [c1].[CourseName], [c1].[CreateDay], [c1].[LecturerId], [c1].[SchoolYear], [c1].[Semester], [c1].[Status], [c1].[SubjectId], [l].[Address], [l].[BirthDate], [l].[Cccd], [l].[CreateDay], [l].[Email], [l].[FacultyId], [l].[FullName], [l].[Gender], [l].[Image], [l].[LecturerCode], [l].[PhoneNumber], [l].[Status], [r].[Building], [r].[CreateDay], [r].[Floor], [r].[Name], [r].[Status], [r].[Vacuity], [c2].[CreateDay], [c2].[EndTime], [c2].[Name], [c2].[StartTime], [c2].[Status]
FROM [ClassSchedule] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Student] AS [s0] ON [c0].[Id] = [s0].[ClassId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [Student] AS [s]
    WHERE [c0].[Id] = [s].[ClassId] AND [s].[StudentCode] = @__username_0)
ORDER BY [c].[EndDay] DESC, [c].[Id], [c0].[Id], [c1].[Id], [l].[Id], [r].[Id], [c2].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ClassId], [c].[ClassShiftId], [c].[CourseId], [c].[CreateDay], [c].[DayOfWeek], [c].[EndDay], [c].[RoomId], [c].[StartDay], [c].[Status], [c0].[Id], [c0].[ClassName], [c0].[CreateDay], [c0].[FacultyId], [c0].[Status], [c1].[Id], [c1].[CourseName], [c1].[CreateDay], [c1].[LecturerId], [c1].[SchoolYear], [c1].[Semester], [c1].[Status], [c1].[SubjectId], [l].[Id], [l].[Address], [l].[BirthDate], [l].[Cccd], [l].[CreateDay], [l].[Email], [l].[FacultyId], [l].[FullName], [l].[Gender], [l].[Image], [l].[LecturerCode], [l].[PhoneNumber], [l].[Status], [r].[Id], [r].[Building], [r].[CreateDay], [r].[Floor], [r].[Name], [r].[Status], [r].[Vacuity], [c2].[Id], [c2].[CreateDay], [c2].[EndTime], [c2].[Name], [c2].[StartTime], [c2].[Status]

INNER JOIN [Class] AS [c0] ON [c].[ClassId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Course] AS [c1] ON [c].[CourseId] = [c1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Lecturer] AS [l] ON [c1].[LecturerId] = [l].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Room] AS [r] ON [c].[RoomId] = [r].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ClassShift] AS [c2] ON [c].[ClassShiftId] = [c2].[Id]
ORDER BY [c].[CreateDay] DESC
